title: Intel Corporation Beats Earnings And Sales Estimates
text: October 13, 2015 at 19:19 PM EDT Intel Corporation Beats Earnings And Sales Estimates Intel (INTC) released its latest earnings report after closing bell tonight, posting earnings of 64 cents per share on $14.5 billion in revenue. Analysts had been expecting earnings of 59 cents per share on $14.22 billion in revenue.
